        "Converge the findings into 4-6 chunky remediation themes, with dependency ordering that separates docs-governance cleanup from Rust contract hardening and RalphMac surface decomposition.",
        "Write `.ralph/cache/followups/RQ-0003.json` in `followups@v1` format with concrete titles, descriptions, scope, evidence, plans, `depends_on_keys`, and independence rationales for each proposed remediation task.",
        "Dry-run the proposal with `ralph task followups apply --task RQ-0003 --dry-run --format json`, fix any schema/dependency issues, then apply it for real through Ralph's normal queue-growth flow.",
